Arashi’s Ohno Satoshi to hold his second art exhibition “FREESTYLE II”

Arahi’s Ohno Satoshi will be holding his second art exhibition “FREESTYLE II” in Tokyo, Omotesando Space O. The exhibit will be held on July 24 – August 23. This comes 7 years after his first art exhibition “FREESTLYE”, which was held in 2008.
